## Glossary Extensions (Unit Testing)

| Term | Means |
|------|-------|
| generating a slug from a title | call: slugify({title}), source: lib/text.tnt, input: test_data.slugify_examples |
| generating a slug from user input | call: slugify({input}), source: lib/text.tnt, input: corpus.strings |
| slug is URL-safe | check: invariant.url_slug |
| slug matches expected format | result is {expected} |
| slug is predictable | property: deterministic |
| slug is stable | property: idempotent |
| generating an excerpt from content | call: truncate_excerpt({content}, {max_length}), source: lib/text.tnt, input: test_data.excerpt_examples |
| generating an excerpt from short content | call: truncate_excerpt({content}, {max_length}), source: lib/text.tnt, input: test_data.excerpt_short |
| excerpt respects the limit | check: invariant.excerpt_length |
| excerpt ends cleanly | check: invariant.excerpt_ending |
| excerpt matches original | result is {expected} |
| excerpt is predictable | property: deterministic |

