## Invariants

Invariant: URL Slug
  id: invariant.url_slug
  description: "A URL-safe slug string"

  Assertions:
    → uses only [a-z0-9-]
    → is lowercase
    → does not start with "-"
    → does not end with "-"
    → does not contain "--"
    → is non-empty

Invariant: Excerpt Length
  id: invariant.excerpt_length
  parameters:
    - max_length: Int
  description: "Excerpt does not exceed maximum length"

  Assertions:
    → length is at most {max_length}

Invariant: Excerpt Ending
  id: invariant.excerpt_ending
  description: "Excerpt ends cleanly (not mid-word)"

  Assertions:
    → ends with "..." or equals original
    → does not end with space before "..."

